WEBVTT

00:01.869 --> 00:03.302
<i> And now, Dickie Dobbins,</i>

00:03.304 --> 00:04.970
<i> with the channel 3</i>
<i> Doppler 12,000</i>

00:04.972 --> 00:07.506
