on current events.

03:54.235 --> 03:56.868
I get most of my news
off Snapple caps.

03:56.870 --> 03:58.403
Please, Francine.

03:58.405 --> 03:59.705
To help a friend.

03:59.707 --> 04:03.609
Sounds like a job
for Suckmachine.

04:03.611 --> 04:05.410
How'd you know
my high school nickname?

04:10.851 --> 04:12.951
Hey, check out what
we found in the basement.

04:12.953 --> 04:14.286
You walk in
without knocking

04:14.288 --> 04:15.587
like a bunch of Duprees?

04:15.589 --> 04:17.222
It's my old
Dream Phone game.

04:17.224 --> 04:19.558
It's so dumb.
You try to figure out

04:19.560 --> 04:21.126
which cute boy
has a crush on you.

04:21.128 --> 04:23.228
We thought it'd be fun
to play as a goof.

04:23.230 --> 04:25.197
Doesn't sound fun.
Sounds lame.

04:25.199 --> 04:26.431
But I guess I'll do it,

04:26.433 --> 04:28.033
'cause I got
nothing else to do.

04:28.035 --> 04:30.035
But it sounds boring.
I'm gonna be bored.

04:30.037 --> 04:32.070
I was right.
This is boring.

04:32.072 --> 04:33.905
I'm bored. I think
I'm just about ready to --

04:33.907 --> 04:36.375
Who is that?!

04:36.377 --> 04:37.776
(breathily) Dylan.
(piano flourish)

04:37.778 --> 04:39.578
(ring)
Hello?

04:39.580 --> 04:41.480
<i> Your crush loves pizza.</i>

04:41.482 --> 04:43.148
That could be Dylan.

04:43.150 --> 04:44.483
We like
all the same things.

04:44.485 --> 04:46.752
Dylan likes the mall.
I like the mall.

04:46.754 --> 04:51.056
Oh, my God.
Is he...the one?

04:51.058 --> 04:53.325
