at the Langley Falls Gator Farm.

05:50.818 --> 05:52.284
Dickie,
I bet you were around

05:52.286 --> 05:53.518
when that oak tree
was planted.

05:53.520 --> 05:54.553
Huh?

05:54.555 --> 05:55.987
Planted?

05:55.989 --> 05:58.056
Dickie was around when
the oak tree was invented.

05:58.058 --> 05:59.725
(chuckle)
Looks like those gators

05:59.727 --> 06:01.059
aren't the only ones
who bite.

06:01.061 --> 06:02.861
Chomp, chomp.
(chuckle)

06:02.863 --> 06:05.197
Her banter -- It's beautiful.

06:05.199 --> 06:09.735
¶ She's a revelatio-o-o-
