of the game.

07:15.602 --> 07:17.469
Now, talk to me, you sicko!

07:17.471 --> 07:19.237
Who are you talking to?
Is it Dylan?

07:19.239 --> 07:21.106
(grunting)

07:21.108 --> 07:22.274
keep your paws off him,
you slut!

07:22.276 --> 07:23.642
(ring)

