07:41.328 --> 07:42.627
to suck
those filthy words back

07:42.629 --> 07:43.929
inside your rotten
little mouth.

07:43.931 --> 07:45.263
Damn it, Roger.

07:45.265 --> 07:46.998
This isn't even
a real person, okay?

07:47.000 --> 07:50.268
