posed for a picture in 1994.

07:50.270 --> 07:51.837
It's insane
to have a crush

07:51.839 --> 07:53.905
on a fake person
on a fake phone.

07:53.907 --> 07:55.907
(sigh)
You're right.

07:55.909 --> 07:57.242
The sane thing to do is

07:57.244 --> 07:59.277
track down the model
who posed for the card

07:59.279 --> 08:00.612
and go on a road trip
to meet him.

08:00.614 --> 08:02.180
