08:32.112 --> 08:34.346
I didn't know
you could die from that.

08:34.348 --> 08:36.281
I thought it just
made you talk funny.

08:36.283 --> 08:38.517
Ah, I had
a stroke, see?

08:38.519 --> 08:40.952
