09:13.754 --> 09:15.554
Thank you, Francine.
That --

09:15.556 --> 09:16.888
That was wonderful.

09:16.890 --> 09:18.356
You just
got in the zone.

09:18.358 --> 09:19.891
It was like there was
no one else at the desk.

09:19.893 --> 09:21.259
Oh! (laughs)

09:21.261 --> 09:22.894
Oh, that's ridiculous.

09:22.896 --> 09:26.264
