down at Larry's.

10:43.810 --> 10:45.310
I was thinking maybe
you could work in

10:45.312 --> 10:46.611
a plug
on the show today.

10:46.613 --> 10:47.946
I'm not gonna
compromise the news

10:47.948 --> 10:49.814
